Troubleshooting
Common Issues and Solutions
Issue 1: Permission denied errors

# Solution: Run with sudo for privileged operations
sudo nmap -sS localhost
sudo netstat -lnp
Issue 2: Python nmap module not found

# Solution: Install using pip3
pip3 install python-nmap
# Or system package manager
sudo apt install python3-nmap
Issue 3: netstat command not found

# Solution: Install net-tools
sudo apt update
sudo apt install net-tools
Issue 4: Slow scanning

# Solution: Use faster timing templates
nmap -T4 localhost  # Aggressive timing
nmap -T5 localhost  # Insane timing (very fast)
